<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New Payment Notification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #007bff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .booking-details { background-color: #333; color: #FFF; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #007bff; color: #FFF; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; }
        .notification { color: #007bff; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #FFF;">New Payment Received! ðŸ’°</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Halo <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <div class="notification">
                <p>ðŸŽ‰ Pembayaran untuk booking baru dengan nomor <strong>{{bookingNo}}</strong> di properti Anda <strong>{{propertyName}}</strong> telah berhasil diterima.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="booking-details">
                <h3 style="color: #007bff; margin-top: 0;">Detail Booking:</h3>
                <p><strong>Nomor Booking:</strong> {{bookingNo}}</p>
                <p><strong>Properti:</strong> {{propertyName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Check-in:</strong> {{checkIn}}</p>
                <p><strong>Check-out:</strong> {{checkOut}}</p>
                <p><strong>Total Pembayaran:</strong> Rp {{totalAmount}}</p>
                <p><strong>Nama User:</strong> {{userName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Email User:</strong> {{userEmail}}</p>
                <p><strong>Metode Pembayaran:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Anda dapat melihat detail booking ini dan mengelola properti Anda melalui dashboard tenant.</p>
            
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{tenantDashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Buka Dashboard Tenant</a>
            </p>
            
            <p>Terima kasih telah menggunakan platform kami!</p>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Hormat kami,<br>Tim {{appName}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
